Move Cards on play field before moving cards from the deck
When you see and ACE card move it to the end field
When a card can be moved to the end field, move it to the end field.
When playing on the play field add and remove cards from the longest row first.
Always move a king to an open space if available
Try and get a king of each color open
if there's nothing playable in the deck, see if you can drag a card from the end field
If there's nothing that can be moved, flip a card from the deck.
Don't move the same card twice in a row.
